<subcellularLocation>
<location>Cell inner membrane</location>
<topology status="potential" evidence="2">Multi-pass membrane protein</topology>
</subcellularLocation>
</comment>
<comment type="induction">
<text evidence="1">Transcriptionally activated by the EnvZ/OmpR regulatory system.</text>
</comment>
<comment type="similarity">
<text>Belongs to the PTR2/POT transporter (TC 2.A.17) family. DtpA subfamily.</text>
</comment>
